<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Gerrymandering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<div class="infobox sisterproject">
<div style="float: left;">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Wiktionary-logo-en.svg" class="image" title="Wiktionary-logo-en.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Wiktionary-logo-en.svg/50px-Wiktionary-logo-en.svg.png" width="50" height="54" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div style="margin-left: 60px;">Look up <i><b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/gerrymander" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:gerrymander">gerrymander</a></b>, <b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/gerrymandering" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:gerrymandering">gerrymandering</a></b></i> in <a href="/wiki/Wiktionary" title="Wiktionary">Wiktionary</a>, the free dictionary.</div>
</div>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.aceproject.org/regions-en/americas/americas-case-studies/chile-constitutional-and-electoral-reform-1998/" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org/regions-en/americas/americas-case-studies/chile-constitutional-and-electoral-reform-1998/" rel="nofollow">Ending the Gerrymander in Chile: the constitutional reforms of 1988</a> — a case study from the <a href="http://www.aceproject.org" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org" rel="nofollow">ACE Project</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.aceproject.org/ace-en/topics/bd/bdy/bdy_my" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org/ace-en/topics/bd/bdy/bdy_my" rel="nofollow">Alleged Gerrymandering in Malaysia: Over-representation of rural districts</a> — an article from the <a href="http://www.aceproject.org" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org" rel="nofollow">ACE Project</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.aceproject.org/ace-en/topics/bd/bdy/bdy_sg" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org/ace-en/topics/bd/bdy/bdy_sg" rel="nofollow">Alleged Gerrymandering in Singapore</a> — an article from the <a href="http://www.aceproject.org" class="external text" title="http://www.aceproject.org" rel="nofollow">ACE Project</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.idea.int/publications/esd/index.cfm" class="external text" title="http://www.idea.int/publications/esd/index.cfm" rel="nofollow">A handbook of electoral system Design</a> from <a href="http://www.idea.int" class="external text" title="http://www.idea.int" rel="nofollow">International IDEA</a></li>
