<li><a href="http://www.abc.net.au/elections/federal/2004/items/200408/s1172393.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.abc.net.au/elections/federal/2004/items/200408/s1172393.htm" rel="nofollow">Anti-Gerrymandering policy in Australia</a></li>
