<li><a href="http://www.commoncensus.org" class="external text" title="http://www.commoncensus.org" rel="nofollow">The CommonCensus Map Project</a> — Draws internal US boundaries based on cultural affinities, not politics</li>
<li><a href="http://www.motherjones.com/news/featurex/2006/09/gerrymander.html" class="external text" title="http://www.motherjones.com/news/featurex/2006/09/gerrymander.html" rel="nofollow">Egregious Cases</a> an article from Mother Jones Magazine</li>
